      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/7/18",
      "text": [
        " اَلرَّجُلِ يَمُوتُ وَ لاَ وَارِثَ لَهُ وَ لاَ مَوْلًى لَهُ فَقَالَ «هُوَ مِنْ أَهْلِ هَذِهِ اَلْآيَةِ «۝ يَسْئَلُونَكَ عَنِ اَلْأَنْفٰالِ ۝» »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1661 - Aban ibn Taghlib narrated from Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) regarding a man who dies without any heirs or any master (to whom he is affiliated):\nThe Imam (as) said: \"He falls under the category mentioned in this verse:\n'They ask you about the spoils (anfal)...' (Surah Al-Anfal 8:1).\""
        ]
      }
    },
